author: adrianc
msg: Asset Maintenance functional change. Maintenance tasks were assigned to the currently logged-in user and there was no way to assign them to other parties. This commit adds that capability, plus it adds asset maintenance specific party roles. The Edit Task screen is much improved.
Internationalization note: this commit contains a new UI label.
